analysis.description:
BWData.addBoostFromTile (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#603-619) uses a dangerous strict equality:
	- _tile.claimer == _attacker
	- _tile.claimer == _defender

BWService.fortifyClaims (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#177-203) does not use the value returned by external calls:
	-address(this).balance.add(_fortifyAmount) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#181-182)

BWService.storeInitialClaim has external calls inside a loop:
	- isNewTile = bwData.isNewTile(tileId) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#168-169)

BWService.storeInitialClaim has external calls inside a loop:
	- bwData.storeClaim(tileId,_msgSender,valuePerBlockInWei) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#176-177)

BWService.fortifyClaims has external calls inside a loop:
	- (claimer,blockValue) = bwData.getTileClaimerAndBlockValue(_claimedTileIds[i]) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#190-192)

BW.claimPrize has external calls inside a loop:
	- tokenOwner = token.ownerOf(tokenId) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#943)

BW.claimPrize has external calls inside a loop:
	- token.safeTransferFrom(tokenOwner,msg.sender,tokenId) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#944)

BW.transferTileFromOwner has external calls inside a loop:
	- claimer = bwData.getCurrentClaimerForTile(tileId) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol)

BW.transferTileFromOwner has external calls inside a loop:
	- bwData.setClaimerForTile(tileId,_newOwner) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol)

Reentrancy in BWService.attackTile (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#228-310):
	External calls:
	- (claimer,blockValue) = bwData.getTileClaimerAndBlockValue(_tileId) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#237)
	- (attackBoost,defendBoost) = bwData.calculateBattleBoost(_tileId,_msgSender,claimer) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#248-250)
	- updateFeeBalance(attackFeeAmount) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#273-274)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- seed (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#275-276)

BWData.addUser (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#511-516) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- require(bool)(user.creationTime == 0) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#513)

BWData.hasUser (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#516-518) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- users[_user].creationTime != 0 (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#517)

BWData.addBoostFromTile (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#603-619) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- require(bool)(_boost.attackBoost + _tile.blockValue >= _tile.blockValue) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#608-612)
	- _tile.claimer == _defender (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#613-618)
	- _tile.claimer == _attacker (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#606-618)
	- require(bool)(_boost.defendBoost + _tile.blockValue >= _tile.blockValue) (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#614-616)

BW.addPrize (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#885-903) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- startTime < block.timestamp (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#890-891)

BW.claimPrize (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#914-945) uses timestamp for comparisons
	Dangerous comparisons:
	- prizeArr[idx].startTime.add(prizeArr[idx].hodlPeriod) <= block.timestamp && lastClaimTime.add(prizeArr[idx].hodlPeriod) <= block.timestamp (/unique_chucks/5/0x6a20d74106f28ad19c60115917ff363ad71f525f.sol#937-945)
